definitions.definition: A violent ejection , such as the spurting out of lava from a volcano .
A sudden release of pressure or tension.
examples: There was an eruption of joy at the final whistle.

definitions.definition: An utterance , especially a sudden one; an ejaculation .
An infection of the skin resulting in a rash or blemishing.
